Project Reflection:

Platforms I Selected:

For my digital portfolio, I created and updated profiles on three important platforms: GitHub, LinkedIn, and Kaggle.

Purpose of Each Platform:

I selected these platforms because each one highlights a different aspect of my skills and helps me build a strong professional presence.

GitHub works like a record of my technical work. It shows my coding skills and demonstrates how I use Git for version control while working on projects.

LinkedIn represents my professional identity. It allows me to showcase my education, connect with professionals, and explore job or internship opportunities.

Kaggle acts as a learning and practice platform. It helps me improve my data science and machine learning skills by working on real-world datasets and participating in competitions.

Overall, using these platforms helps me present my abilities more effectively and prepares me for future career opportunities.
